Dialogue: 9,0:02:46.01,0:02:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kobato-chan là bé thiên thần!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cho chị liếm cái nào!
